---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | Codestri">
  <section class="py-14">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-violet-300">Services</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-5xl font-black">Focused services for modern web growth.</h1>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-300/20 bg-slate-900/45 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Landing Page Rebuilds</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">Transform outdated pages into modern conversion engines with clean UI and stronger CTA flow.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-300/20 bg-slate-900/45 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Performance Optimization</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">Improve load speed, Core Web Vitals, and responsiveness to reduce bounce and improve trust.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-300/20 bg-slate-900/45 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Content & UX Refinement</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">Restructure page content and visual hierarchy so visitors understand and act quickly.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-300/20 bg-slate-900/45 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Ongoing Iteration Support</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">Incremental improvements based on behavior, feedback, and measurable business goals.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
